Step What to do

1. Sign in Go to https://platform.openai.com and log in
with your OpenAl account. (If you don't have

keys”.
3. Create a new key Press “Create new secret key” > give it a

label such as “excuse-generator” > Create.

**4. Copy immediately Click “Copy”. You'll never be able to see it
again once you close the modal.
